【Saveur Classic At Home 🏡】
@saveursg recently launched their online food delivery store - ”shop.saveur.sg” offering Islandwide Delivery.
With this one-stop-shop, they are offering their Signature dishes & Ice Cream from their 4️⃣ Concepts namely Saveur, MediumRare, FrapasBar and Bread & Butterfly. 👄Tried their 🆕Saveur Classic 4 course meal $50+ @saveursg which consists of :
◾️Soup - French Onion Soup
◾️💋Starter - Saveur Pasta
◾️💋Main - Saveur Signature Duck Confit ◾️💋Dessert - Pistachio Panna Cotta 
Love their signature Saveur pasta & duck confit, end the meal with their yummy pistachio Panna Cotta dessert 😋!
Sound interesting & value for money right ? 
Quickly action NOW if you craving for French cuisines & do not want to leave your comfort safe home zone during this “Circuit Breaker “ period!
📣Quote “ NIKOLAI10OFF ”  Promo code - 
Orders made in May and June will enjoy a 10% 💥off all orders in top of ongoing promotions.
🌐https://shop.saveur.sg⁣

Remember stay home stay safe stay healthy & don’t any how run outside hor 😉!
